    <h2 id="intro">Introducing the town：</h2>
    <article>
        <p>
            Guangzhou is a city located in Guangdong Province in southern China, with a population of approximately 15 million people<em>It is known for its Cantonese cuisine and beautiful scenery in the Pearl River Delta</em>
             It is known for its Cantonese cuisine and beautiful scenery in the Pearl River Delta. Guangzhou is also one of the centers of business in China、with many companies having their headquarters there. Guangzhou South Railway Station is a central hub in China's high-speed railway network, providing convenient access to surrounding cities and Hong Kong.
        </p>
    </article>
